Description: Carry your laptop computer and other business or school essentials neatly and stylishly in the McKlein USA W Series Willow Springs Leather Ladies' Briefcase. This luxurious yet affordable Italian leather bag offers structure and enough room for all your business or personal necessities. It has a top zip closure and opens to reveal a spacious, center zipper-compartment-divided main compartment with a padded laptop computer pocket generous enough to accommodate your books, binders, folders, and files. A separate, zippered organizational compartment contains a logo patch, pen loops, a cell phone pocket, a multipurpose slide pocket, and a zippered compartment for keeping valuables safe and secure. The McKlein USA W Series Willow Springs Leather Ladies' Briefcase has sturdy hardware and dual straps for carrying comfort. Front pocket with a magnetic snap holds small accessories. Two side pockets for small miscellaneous items. Back pocket for accessories. Main compartment features an interior zipper pocket and an interior organizer for pens, business cards and small devices. Built-in high-density compartment protects laptops up to 15.4” in screen size. Leather shoulder straps. Orange, green, blue, and pink cases are trimmed in sand.
